msgstr "Filial yoki randevu topilmadi."

msgid "You already have a booking for this slot."
msgstr "Sizda ushbu vaqt uchun allaqachon bron mavjud."

msgid "This car is already booked for this slot."
msgstr "Bu mashina ushbu vaqt uchun allaqachon band qilingan."

msgid "This time slot is already full."
msgstr "Ushbu vaqt bandi allaqachon to'ldirilgan."

